      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Charmed by a Queen",
        "Client": "Reckless Artist",
        "Description": "Hunter Hunter HUNTER! We must\r\ngo at once! As we speak the queen\r\nherself is gracing the Shrine Ruins!\r\nI must capture her majesty in all its\r\nglory! But I hear Rathian are rather...\r\ndifficult to work with. Perhaps you\r\ncan assist me?",
        "Target": "Hunt a Rathian",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Le charme d\u0027une reine",
        "Client": "Artiste t\u00E9m\u00E9raire",
        "Description": "Il faut qu\u0027on se d\u00E9p\u00EAche ! La reine\r\nest au Temple oubli\u00E9 en ce moment\r\nm\u00EAme ! Je dois absolument\r\nl\u0027immortaliser dans toute sa\r\nsplendeur ! Mais il para\u00EEt que les\r\nRathian ne se laissent pas faire...\r\nEst-ce que tu pourrais m\u0027aider ?",
